commit.message:
xm-mingw32.h (HOST_BIT_BUCKET): Define as "nul".

	* config/i386/xm-mingw32.h (HOST_BIT_BUCKET): Define
	as "nul".
	* config/i386/xm-mingw32.h: Change GNU CC to GCC.

From-SVN: r69434
